<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I am refuting the Pseudoscience surrounding the nuclear devices and the pusher plate assembly.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
How are you defining &quot;pseudoscience&quot; with regards to the information that has been discussed and the documents/links provided..?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>pseu·do·sci·ence <br>
n. <br>
A theory, methodology, or practice that is considered to be without scientific foundation.<br>
<br>
pseudo·scien·tific adj. <br>
pseudo·scien·tist n.<br>
<br>
Source: The American Heritage® Dictionary of the English Language, Fourth Edition<br>
Copyright © 2000 by Houghton Mifflin Company.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<br>
***  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>edit:  Photon comment withdrawn, apologies.  Tho', it is a rather broad term to use when referring to specific electromagnetic spectra.. Mind you, it is extremely unlikely that the high (Gamma, Neutrons, X-rays) radiation would &quot;degrade the pusher plate quickly enough to make it unusable&quot; as it reacts with matter only rarely and with great infrequency (as per a link referenced in a following post)</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> ***<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>(BTW, where do we get the idea that the shaped &amp; directed plasma jets are carriers of Gamma rays and other hard penetrating radiation which could damage the metal plate?)<br>
<br>
Uh-nuclear detonations. Look it up yourself.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.dodsbir.net/awardlist/sttr1_98.htm">Not nuclear, but plasma related..quote to follow..</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> The energy efficiency of the device is similar to that of pulsed plasma thrusters, and the electronics simpler. Specific impulse Isp is adjustable, and Isp=7000 sec has been measured. The plume produced by this interaction will be a high-velocity, electrically neutral, directed plasma jet, not a cloud of chemical compounds that can condense on the spacecraft. <br>
